# Security Audit (CSO)

1. OWASP Top-10 scan against codebase
2. STRIDE threat model for new features
3. Secrets grep (API keys, tokens, passwords in code)
4. Supply chain check (dependency vulnerabilities)
5. Output: severity-ranked findings report
